  {
    question: 'What features should dog daycare software have?',
    answer: 'Essential features include: online booking with real-time availability, capacity management by playgroup or weight class, vaccination tracking with automatic expiry alerts, activity logs with photo uploads, automated email and SMS reminders, integrated payment processing, add-on and upsell capabilities, and mobile-responsive access. Owner portal and SMS reminders complete the set for facilities wanting to eliminate phone calls entirely. Facilities running mixed services (daycare + boarding + grooming) should look for a unified platform to avoid switching between multiple systems.',
    links: [
      { text: 'Pet Grooming Software', url: '/pet-grooming-software/' }
    ]
