        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-brand-navy mb-2">How Tails & Trails Cut Admin from 3 Hours to 45 Minutes a Day</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-500 mb-8 text-sm">Bristol dog daycare · 28-dog capacity · switched from Google Sheets + WhatsApp</p>

        <div class="bg-gray-50 border border-gray-200 rounded-xl p-8 mb-8">
          <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-6 mb-8">
            <div class="text-center">
              <p class="text-3xl font-bold text-brand-red">−2h 15m</p>
